Comment: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,-------OPCN_START-------
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:26.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}从今往后的事 I will be there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:32.62,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}那天以后的事 With me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:36.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}夕阳西下之时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:42.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}追逐着渐渐消失的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:48.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}谁都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:52.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}时光无法回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:57.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}呈现在眼前的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:01.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}毫无疑问的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:11.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}真正想见的人 在道路的另一头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:14.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}为了追逐那天的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:17.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}迈出了脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:24.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}这前面是无法成歌的Stories
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:28.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}I can’t tell what’s going on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:35.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}现在还不是寻找答案的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:40.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}现在已经无需用声音表达
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:45.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}只要怀着心愿向前
